To process the user request and filter out data pertaining to the species "Mus musculus," we can construct a query to exclude such data. Below is an example of how to structure this query:

```json
{
  "query": {
    "columnSelection": [
      {
        "concreteType": "org.sagebionetworks.repo.model.grid.query.SelectAll"
      }
    ],
    "filters": [
      {
        "concreteType": "org.sagebionetworks.repo.model.grid.query.CellValueFilter",
        "columnName": "species",
        "operator": "NOT_EQUALS",
        "value": "Mus musculus"
      }
    ],
    "limit": 100
  }
}
```

### Explanation:
