   - `operator`: Defines the comparison operator (`NOT_EQUALS`).
   - `value`: The value to compare against (`Mus musculus`).

This query will retrieve all columns but exclude any data where the species is "Mus musculus," fulfilling the user's request. If you need further modifications or have more requests, feel free to ask!

